As well as having your {locl} feature, You have to have your language declaration in the very bottom window on the feature section of the OT tab:

languagesystem DFLT dflt;  
languagesystem latn dflt;  
languagesystem latn MOL;  
languagesystem latn ROM;  
languagesystem latn AZE;  
languagesystem latn CRT;  
languagesystem latn TRK;

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20100203094107im_/http:/typophile.com/files/loclfeature_5285.png)

ChrisL
